{
  "stem": "4753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then-- because many of the children were thrown into the flame, grabbed from the mother's arm and thrown into the flame.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But naturally, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't know where we are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then some of the girls around me started to scream that they are burning us alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then we realized that the stench, what we feels, is the burning flesh of human, and the fat of human, and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's what happened in the first night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When we came to the barracks, the girls started to-- I, I didn't speak for three weeks, not one word, after that scene.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the girls came into the barracks where we were sent, they were screaming and crying, where are our parents and sisters and brothers?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of the SS men walked up and with the rubber stick pointed to the sky and said, look up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what we have seen, very heavy black smoke covering the whole sky.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was laughing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, there are your sisters and parents, and there where you are going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he turned around and walked away, laughing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even today, many times I hear the laugh.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That was my first day in Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I was the only one from my whole family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even I did go into with a lot of uncles and aunts, cousins, and nephews the very same night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was the only survivor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was five months in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
